---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="47-Point PI Firm AI Audit Checklist"
  description="Free download: the 47-Point PI Firm AI Audit Checklist — Red/Yellow/Green scoring across intake, demand letters, pleadings, discovery, medical records, and advertising."
  noIndex={false}
>
  <article class="aie-capture">
    <div class="container">

      <header class="aie-capture__header">
        <p class="label"><a href="/ai-ethics">Ethics Safe AI Use for Law Firms</a></p>
        <h1 class="aie-capture__title">The PI Firm AI Audit Checklist</h1>
        <p class="aie-capture__sub">
          47 risk points scored Red/Yellow/Green across intake, demand letters,
          pleadings, discovery, medical records, and advertising. Free download.
        </p>
      </header>

      <hr class="rule" />

      <div class="aie-capture__body">
        <div class="prose">
          <p>
            Each item identifies a specific exposure, the rule or opinion that
            creates it, and the policy document required to close it. Run it
            with your ops manager. Any Red item requires immediate attention.
            Any Yellow item requires a written protocol.
          </p>
          <p>
            The expanded version — with remediation steps and policy templates
            for every item — is in the
            <a href="/ai-ethics">full playbook</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- CONNECT TO ESP: replace this form with your ESP embed code -->
        <!-- Suggested fields: first_name, email, firm_name (optional) -->
        <!-- Tag subscriber: lead-magnet-checklist, ca-pi-firm (if geo confirmed) -->
        <!-- Redirect after submit to: /ai-ethics/thanks (create separately) -->
        <form class="aie-form" action="#" method="POST">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="first_name">First name</label>
            <input type="text" id="first_name" name="first_name" placeholder="First name" required />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Work email</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="you@yourfirm.com" required />
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary">Send me the checklist</button>
          <p class="aie-form__note">
            No spam. One email with the checklist, then a short series on the
            six highest-risk areas for PI firms. Unsubscribe any time.
          </p>
        </form>
      </div>

      <hr class="rule" />

      <p class="aie-capture__disclaimer">
        <em>Informational only. Not legal advice. Ethics rules vary by jurisdiction.</em><br>
        Christian Kameir &thinsp;·&thinsp; © 2026 Decentralized Publishing LLC. All rights reserved.
      </p>

    </div>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
.aie-capture__header {
  padding-top: 4rem;
  padding-bottom: var(--space-m);
}

.aie-capture__title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.1;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  color: var(--text);
  margin-top: 0.75rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.aie-capture__sub {
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.75;
  max-width: 480px;
}

.aie-capture__body {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 4rem;
  padding-block: var(--space-l);
  align-items: start;
}

.aie-form {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1.25rem;
}

.aie-form__note {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.6;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em;
}

.aie-capture__disclaimer {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.7;
  padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);
}

@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .aie-capture__body {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-m);
  }
}
</style>
